snippet.title: Amphibia Locust Pocus (Disney Games)
snippet.description: Locust Pocus is an online game released on DisneyNOW and was developed by Workinman. The game focuses on Anne Boonchuy and her trusty sidekick Sprig Plantar as they go on an adventure to get the townsfolk to like Hop Pop again and get him out of his cell.
